{"tid":1010084,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"做做吓，港豬變……","createTime":"2019-02-05T16:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T16:35:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"770adfd5da9151dfe61431ffa560ccf0869a61f0","tid":1010084,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190205/20606520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190205%2F20606520&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=f63860fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190205%2F20606520&h=b11ac271\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190205/20606520</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月05日 <br />\n<br />\n做做吓，港豬變&hellip;&hellip; - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190205/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190205%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=af37a093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n送狗迎豬前夕，警隊一哥的金句雖然及不上四點鐘許Sir，唔值得recap成英文，但也頗堪港豬玩味。一哥對上升55%的警察犯罪率頗為不滿，因而說「我地警察嚟㗎嘛，做咩做做吓，做咗賊呢。」<br />\n<br />\n由當差變做賊，的確叫人遺憾。同一片天空下，一樣有人浩歎，點解我地做領導人㗎嘛，做咩做做吓做咗階下囚呢。<br />\n<br />\n更加令港豬感慨的是，做咩有人做做吓做了監躉，但有人犯相似的罪，額頭鑿住個賊字，依然被放生呢。明明係司法機關，做咩做做吓，做咗掠水神棍，公開表演盲目放生呢。龜和魚放生不得其法，害人害物㗎嘛，師奶都懂的道理，做咩做到最高級的法律才俊，會翻白眼鳩噏獻醜呢。<br />\n<br />\n做做吓人變狼，做做吓大學生變鬼，做做吓60歲變中年，做做吓一國兩制變一制，做做吓港豬變23條粉腸。原來，警察做做吓「做世界」是有苦衷的。  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n可能香港也要起圍牆 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n新　禧 (尊子)"}]}